{
  "stem": "12768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And from there, they were sent on to Auschwitz, and maybe some to Belsen and other extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And so there was those two things that my mother had seen in the-- in this room that she had stacked things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There was a prayer book, which was a book that, when it opened, it opened on the page.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And inside was two things that was pressed in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was a four leaf clover and an edelweiss, which was a song, Edelweiss, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my mother took [INAUDIBLE] when she saw that, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She said-- she put the [INAUDIBLE] book aside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then there was a front shawl of a Catholic priest, which she saw was a beautiful brocade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And she had put those aside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she went-- and she said, I'll be back in a minute, and she went into her workplace.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And even though the German was standing outside, she packed up the book and the shawl in a piece of paper, you know, and walked out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the Germans never said anything to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And she went up on a bus, and she took this with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Anyway, she came back-- I will talk about those two things later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But she-- they boarded the bus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And she never really told me how many days it took to drive to Germany, first Czechoslovakia and then Germany, into Hamburg, or around Hamburg, and up to southern Schleswig and then into Denmark, across Denmark, and then they were ferried across to Sweden, because the war was still raging.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And my mother said that every so often, they stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "That was when there was bombings of Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And so the buses stopped, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And the buses otherwise never stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There was two chauffeurs on each bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
